      \begin {tikzcd}
        \hat {C}(yA, F)\ar [d, "\beta _*"']\ar [r, "\Phi _F"] & FA\ar [d, "\beta _A"] \\
        \hat {C}(yA, G)\ar [r, "\Phi _G"'] & GA
      \end {tikzcd}


commutes, as demonstrated by 




